items.title: BLOND:ISH x KeeQ Feat. Chloe Paige – The Cure (Extended Mix)
items.description: Canadian DJ, producer, record label head and environmental activist BLOND:ISH makes her anticipated debut on Defected alongside rising UK star KeeQ with ‘The Cure’. Soaked in the sunshine-filled, Latin-infused style BLOND:ISH’s DJ sets are known for, a blissful combination with KeeQ’s signature tribal and emotive elements as Chloe Paige’s distorted vocal purrs over hypnotic whirrs and a low swung bassline for an unmissable label debut from a triptych of house talent.
